      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my absolute favorite ride. This car has been my pride and joy, and it\u2019s honestly a dream to drive\u2014there's just nothing like the way it handles the open road. It\u2019s been kept in really solid shape; it\u2019s got a few tiny 'character marks' from some great adventures, but she still looks stunning in the driveway and runs like a top. I\u2019ve taken care of it like family, and I\u2019m sure the next owner is going to have just as much fun as I did. Come by, grab a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
